}

api for checking account details:
get method
localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/user/

api for creating list
post method
localhost:8000/lists/create/
body
{
	"list_name":"final check."
}

api for viewing all list
get method
localhost:8000/api/v1/lists

api for viewing particular list
get method
localhost:8000/api/v1/lists/1/

api for delete list
delete method
localhost:8000/api/v1/lists/24

api for edit list only for author
put method
localhost:8000/api/v1/lists/24
body
{
	"list_name":"Imagine dragons songs list."
}

api for viewing all tasks of user
get method
localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/all/

